and let her reply to your text in person.

291
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,330
Thank you, Mr. Yang.

292
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:21,240
Wait a minute.

293
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:27,400
I've laid out the rainbow bridge for you.

294
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:29,720
Whether you can reach the shore of happiness

295
00:18:29,720 --> 00:18:30,920
depends on yourself.

296
00:18:32,360 --> 00:18:33,960
Memorize the products well.

297
00:18:34,040 --> 00:18:35,000
I will do my best.

298
00:18:58,840 --> 00:18:59,370
How is it?

299
00:19:00,200 --> 00:19:01,730
The scene is not bad, right?

300
00:19:02,840 --> 00:19:04,120
It's just an internal dinner,

301
00:19:04,120 --> 00:19:05,580
isn't it too extravagant?

302
00:19:07,320 --> 00:19:09,320
Isn't this for the investors to see?

303
00:19:10,680 --> 00:19:12,000
Honestly, Mr. Li.

304
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:13,680
With this investment,

305
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:14,520
the way the process is going,

306
00:19:14,520 --> 00:19:15,980
I'm losing my confidence.

307
00:19:16,320 --> 00:19:17,850
Why don't you give me a hint?

308
00:19:18,200 --> 00:19:19,720
If you really plan to give it to Lu Li,

309
00:19:19,720 --> 00:19:21,720
I can at least be mentally prepared.

310
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:23,440
Ms. Ai Wei.

311
00:19:23,560 --> 00:19:25,320
I heard what you just said.

312
00:19:25,320 --> 00:19:26,720
You're being too modest.

313
00:19:26,760 --> 00:19:27,680
After all, behind you,

314
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:29,540
there are 20 million of your fans.

315
00:19:29,760 --> 00:19:31,120
Who's being modest?

316
00:19:31,240 --> 00:19:32,320
When it comes to capability,

317
00:19:32,320 --> 00:19:35,120
none of those 20 million can compare to you, Mr. Lu.

318
00:19:35,680 --> 00:19:37,640
Otherwise, after I fired you,

319
00:19:37,640 --> 00:19:39,200
how could you get recruited by Mr. Li,

320
00:19:39,200 --> 00:19:40,760
and still be so successful?

321
00:19:42,040 --> 00:19:43,570
I wouldn't say I'm capable.

322
00:19:44,040 --> 00:19:45,370
I just have a thick skin.

323
00:19:48,320 --> 00:19:49,120
You two,

324
00:19:49,880 --> 00:19:51,520
one is the face of the company,

325
00:19:51,520 --> 00:19:52,960
and the other is the operations director.

326
00:19:52,960 --> 00:19:54,690
You are both my right-hand men.

327
00:19:54,760 --> 00:19:56,290
The company can't function

328
00:19:56,400 --> 00:19:57,660
without either of you.

329
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:00,600
Besides, 1001 Nights

330
00:20:00,880 --> 00:20:02,010
and Liguang Company

331
00:20:02,160 --> 00:20:03,820
are in a healthy competition.

332
00:20:04,320 --> 00:20:04,680
Yeah.

333
00:20:05,320 --> 00:20:07,650
Even without the 200 million investment,

334
00:20:07,720 --> 00:20:09,450
getting to learn from Ms. Ai Wei

335
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,200
makes it all worth it.

336
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:12,640
Mr. Li.

337
00:20:23,840 --> 00:20:26,040
False modesty is just slick

338
00:20:26,560 --> 00:20:27,360
and annoying.

339
00:20:29,520 --> 00:20:31,520
I mean it from the bottom of my heart.

340
00:20:32,760 --> 00:20:34,360
An enemy is the best teacher.

341
00:20:37,280 --> 00:20:37,960
Look,

342
00:20:38,560 --> 00:20:40,420
who do you think he'll call first?

343
00:20:43,680 --> 00:20:44,480
Neither of us.

344
00:20:45,280 --> 00:20:47,610
Doesn't he love to be strictly impartial?

345
00:20:47,920 --> 00:20:48,960
As a boss,

346
00:20:48,960 --> 00:20:52,420
watching subordinates infight gives him a sense of security.

347
00:20:52,560 --> 00:20:53,690
He claims to be fair,

348
00:20:54,360 --> 00:20:55,960
but he has his own judgments.

349
00:20:57,040 --> 00:20:57,640
Mr. Zhang.

350
00:20:59,880 --> 00:21:00,400
Mr. Li.

351
00:21:01,480 --> 00:21:02,200
Good evening.

352
00:21:02,200 --> 00:21:03,000
Good evening.

353
00:21:04,320 --> 00:21:05,720
This is your company's top talent.

354
00:21:05,720 --> 00:21:06,680
Yes.

355
00:21:06,800 --> 00:21:07,480
Good job.

356
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:12,160
You trained Weiwei well.

357
00:21:12,800 --> 00:21:14,800
She even dares to chat up investors.

358
00:21:17,360 --> 00:21:19,420
Miss Ai Wei, you feel threatened too?

359
00:21:19,880 --> 00:21:20,810
But don't worry.

360
00:21:21,280 --> 00:21:23,720
After all, you have a perfect marriage to support you.

361
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:25,120
She can't compare to you.

362
00:21:27,320 --> 00:21:29,180
Why would I compare myself to her?

363
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:38,320
The 16/17 Lafite tastes better.

364
00:21:38,560 --> 00:21:39,560
The yield is high.

365
00:21:39,880 --> 00:21:41,610
Most importantly, it's cheap.

366
00:21:42,800 --> 00:21:43,920
The 82 Lafite

367
00:21:43,920 --> 00:21:45,840
just profited from the first wave of dividends.

368
00:21:45,840 --> 00:21:46,840
It's just a bluff.

369
00:21:47,480 --> 00:21:50,010
I think it will be eliminated sooner or later.

370
00:22:02,520 --> 00:22:02,960
Mr. Li.

371
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:04,160
Weiwei.

372
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:06,800
Learn more from Mr. Li.

373
00:22:06,800 --> 00:22:08,130
Ask him for more advice.

374
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:09,840
You were able to develop to where you are today

375
00:22:09,840 --> 00:22:10,680
all because of Mr. Li.

376
00:22:10,680 --> 00:22:11,960
And with Mr. Zhang's support,

377
00:22:11,960 --> 00:22:12,480
right?

378
00:22:14,080 --> 00:22:14,680
You are too kind.

379
00:22:14,680 --> 00:22:15,280
Mr. Zhang.

380
00:22:39,640 --> 00:22:40,240
Luo Xin.

381
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:41,560
I'm going to order takeout.

382
00:22:41,560 --> 00:22:42,280
I'm hungry.

383
00:22:42,280 --> 00:22:43,480
Wanna split an order?

384
00:22:46,760 --> 00:22:47,220
Luo Xin,

385
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:52,480
why aren't you saying anything?

386
00:22:52,600 --> 00:22:53,660
I'm talking to you.

387
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:56,140
Luo Xin.

388
00:22:56,440 --> 00:22:58,440
I'm ordering food. Do you want some?

389
00:22:59,160 --> 00:23:00,000
I have a fever.

390
00:23:02,360 --> 00:23:02,920
A fever?

391
00:23:09,800 --> 00:23:10,930
You do feel a bit hot.

392
00:23:11,320 --> 00:23:12,780
Did you take any medicine?

393
00:23:12,800 --> 00:23:13,400
No.

394
00:23:14,600 --> 00:23:15,640
Are you an idiot?

395
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:17,970
You have a fever but didn't take medicine.

396
00:24:03,240 --> 00:24:05,120
I still have to take care of you when it counts.

397
00:24:05,120 --> 00:24:06,650
Do you think I'm your nanny?

398
00:24:16,800 --> 00:24:17,530
Listen to me.

399
00:24:18,280 --> 00:24:19,120
I diluted it a bit.

400
00:24:19,120 --> 00:24:20,720
This is to lower your temperature.

401
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:22,400
Remember to wipe yourself down.

402
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:24,060
I'll go buy you some medicine.

403
00:25:15,080 --> 00:25:15,480
Luo Xin.

404
00:25:15,480 --> 00:25:17,140
Why didn't you wipe yourself?

405
00:25:21,200 --> 00:25:22,200
It's gone cold.

406
00:25:49,040 --> 00:25:49,520
Come on.

407
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:50,640
Get up.

408
00:25:51,640 --> 00:25:52,500
Let me wipe you.

409
00:25:54,680 --> 00:25:55,520
Get up.

410
00:26:01,120 --> 00:26:02,050
Not moving, huh?

411
00:26:03,720 --> 00:26:05,580
Then I'm taking off your blanket.

412
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:13,760
I'm taking off your clothes.

413
00:26:19,760 --> 00:26:20,560
You're the one not moving.

414
00:26:20,560 --> 00:26:21,960
I don't want to take advantage of you.

415
00:26:21,960 --> 00:26:23,280
I'm just saving a life.

416
00:26:30,040 --> 00:26:31,640
You're usually so mean to me,

417
00:26:32,160 --> 00:26:33,280
and so stingy.

418
00:26:35,440 --> 00:26:38,040
But at critical times, I still have to save you.

419
00:27:02,520 --> 00:27:04,380
I'm going to unbutton your shirt.

420
00:27:22,560 --> 00:27:23,960
If it weren't for the fact

421
00:27:24,800 --> 00:27:25,800
that you're about to die

422
00:27:25,800 --> 00:27:27,600
and no one would split the rent with me,

423
00:27:27,600 --> 00:27:28,730
I wouldn't save you.

424
00:27:35,640 --> 00:27:37,000
I'm going to wipe your back.

425
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:38,060
Please cooperate.

426
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:45,240
One, two, three.

427
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:50,250
One, two.

428
00:27:52,480 --> 00:27:53,560
Help!

429
00:27:54,760 --> 00:27:55,880
You are so heavy.

430
00:28:06,920 --> 00:28:08,760
Let's see how you thank me later.

431
00:28:21,840 --> 00:28:23,240
Take the medicine later.

432
00:28:25,920 --> 00:28:27,780
I'll treat you to a meal tomorrow.

433
00:28:31,600 --> 00:28:32,480
Oh, you.

434
00:28:32,480 --> 00:28:33,600
Are you faking it?

435
00:28:33,960 --> 00:28:34,440
Luo Xin.

436
00:28:34,960 --> 00:28:36,080
Wake up, Luo Xin.

437
00:28:36,080 --> 00:28:37,080
Are you faking it?

438
00:28:37,080 --> 00:28:38,340
I'm really burning up.

439
00:28:38,400 --> 00:28:39,200
You can talk, right?

440
00:28:39,200 --> 00:28:40,720
Get up and take your medicine.

441
00:28:40,720 --> 00:28:41,120
Get up.

442
00:28:41,800 --> 00:28:43,520
Get up right now.

443
00:28:47,640 --> 00:28:48,100
Take it.

444
00:28:49,160 --> 00:28:50,000
Take it.

445
00:28:51,320 --> 00:28:53,000
Do you expect me to feed you your medicine?

446
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:53,460
Take it.

447
00:28:54,040 --> 00:28:55,100
Drink it yourself.

448
00:29:23,640 --> 00:29:24,880
Do you take me for a nanny?

449
00:29:24,880 --> 00:29:25,740
In your dreams.

450
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:07,060
You're up so early.

451
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:09,730
Looks like you're back to life.

452
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:10,840
Don't worry.

453
00:30:10,840 --> 00:30:11,840
I didn't take advantage of you.

454
00:30:11,840 --> 00:30:13,300
Your innocence is intact.

455
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:16,800
About yesterday,

456
00:30:17,320 --> 00:30:17,960
thank you.

457
00:30:20,520 --> 00:30:22,580
It was no trouble. No need to thank me.

458
00:30:23,760 --> 00:30:25,420
It's still quite early today.

459
00:30:25,440 --> 00:30:26,920
Let's have breakfast together.

460
00:30:26,920 --> 00:30:27,450
My treat.

461
00:30:28,800 --> 00:30:29,130
Sure.

462
00:30:38,320 --> 00:30:38,920
Your turn.

463
00:30:52,640 --> 00:30:52,970
Here.

464
00:30:53,400 --> 00:30:54,000
Thank you.

465
00:30:57,880 --> 00:30:59,040
This is so lavish.

466
00:30:59,520 --> 00:31:01,280
I've been in Beijing for several months.

467
00:31:01,280 --> 00:31:02,640
I haven't eaten any of this.

468
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:03,440
Let me tell you.

469
00:31:03,440 --> 00:31:04,040
Nowadays in Beijing,

470
00:31:04,040 --> 00:31:05,240
it's hard to find a proper

471
00:31:05,240 --> 00:31:06,570
place to eat breakfast.

472
00:31:07,000 --> 00:31:08,130
And I still feel that

473
00:31:08,240 --> 00:31:09,760
sitting down to eat breakfast in the morning

474
00:31:09,760 --> 00:31:11,360
is how the day really begins.

475
00:31:12,600 --> 00:31:14,040
Usually, the people who come at this time

476
00:31:14,040 --> 00:31:15,640
are mostly old men and women.

477
00:31:15,680 --> 00:31:17,010
The small talk they have

478
00:31:17,120 --> 00:31:18,250
sounds so friendly.

479
00:31:20,360 --> 00:31:20,920
You,

480
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:22,400
you seem pretty boring usually.

481
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:24,600
I didn't expect you to love life so much.

482
00:31:27,760 --> 00:31:28,620
Smells so good.

483
00:31:29,800 --> 00:31:32,060
I haven't eaten breakfast in a long time.

484
00:31:33,200 --> 00:31:34,530
You're usually so busy.

485
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:36,220
I still don't know,

486
00:31:36,520 --> 00:31:37,320
what do you do?

487
00:31:38,640 --> 00:31:39,570
A video blogger.

488
00:31:40,800 --> 00:31:42,060
I just use the platform

489
00:31:42,200 --> 00:31:43,930
to share my life with everyone.

490
00:31:44,800 --> 00:31:46,840
Do you know Meiduo from Xinghe Video?

491
00:31:46,840 --> 00:31:47,500
I know that.

492
00:31:48,760 --> 00:31:50,490
But what happens if we succeed?

493
00:31:50,600 --> 00:31:52,040
You could be like Aiwei.

494
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:53,800
You'd have tens of millions of fans,

495
00:31:53,800 --> 00:31:55,730
and everyone could see your posts.

496
00:31:55,840 --> 00:31:56,640
Sounds great.

497
00:31:57,320 --> 00:31:58,120
It's not easy.

498
00:32:09,720 --> 00:32:10,720
Why don't you eat the yolk?

499
00:32:10,720 --> 00:32:11,780
It's so delicious.

500
00:32:12,760 --> 00:32:14,360
The cholesterol is too high.

501
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:20,860
What about you?

502
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:24,160
I have a younger sister.

503
00:32:24,160 --> 00:32:25,840
She's loved egg yolks since she was little.

504
00:32:25,840 --> 00:32:27,840
So I always gave mine to her when we were kids.

505
00:32:27,840 --> 00:32:29,680
After I grew up and made money to buy my own eggs,

506
00:32:29,680 --> 00:32:30,810
I only eat the yolks.

507
00:32:42,560 --> 00:32:44,090
We make a pretty good match.

508
00:32:52,200 --> 00:32:52,800
By the way,

509
00:32:53,280 --> 00:32:54,940
how do you usually get to work?

510
00:32:55,320 --> 00:32:55,920
By subway.

511
00:32:57,120 --> 00:32:58,320
I take the subway too.

512
00:32:59,200 --> 00:33:00,160
Which line do you take?

513
00:33:00,160 --> 00:33:00,640
Line 14.

514
00:33:01,760 --> 00:33:02,760
I take Line 14 too.

515
00:33:03,360 --> 00:33:04,490
What a coincidence!

516
00:34:44,320 --> 00:34:44,800
Hello, everyone.

517
00:34:44,800 --> 00:34:47,040
Today I'm attending the wedding of my college classmate

518
00:34:47,040 --> 00:34:49,719
and best friend, Lin Xiaoxiao.

519
00:34:50,320 --> 00:34:50,880
Look, everyone.

520
00:34:50,880 --> 00:34:51,880
Her wedding dress

521
00:34:52,120 --> 00:34:53,159
is so beautiful.

522
00:34:54,159 --> 00:34:55,080
Twinkling,

523
00:34:55,199 --> 00:34:56,159
like a fairy.

524
00:34:58,040 --> 00:34:59,640
When we were in school, she always said

525
00:34:59,640 --> 00:35:00,400
that her wedding

526
00:35:00,400 --> 00:35:02,480
must be a dreamy one.

527
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:06,130
Let's take a look at our main character today, Xiaoxiao.

528
00:35:06,280 --> 00:35:07,340
Say hi to everyone.

529
00:35:07,800 --> 00:35:08,920
Hello, everyone.

530
00:35:09,120 --> 00:35:10,320
Isn't she beautiful?

531
00:35:11,440 --> 00:35:11,970
Haofeng.

532
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:14,040
Old Wu.

533
00:35:14,040 --> 00:35:14,360
Sister-in-law.

534
00:35:14,360 --> 00:35:15,200
Congratulations to you.

535
00:35:15,200 --> 00:35:15,930
You're here.

536
00:35:16,120 --> 00:35:16,880
Thank you.

537
00:35:16,880 --> 00:35:17,560
Congratulations to you too, sister-in-law.

538
00:35:17,560 --> 00:35:18,280
Thank you.

539
00:35:19,320 --> 00:35:20,040
I heard

540
00:35:20,040 --> 00:35:21,300
your son Wuhan is back.

541
00:35:21,960 --> 00:35:22,240
Where is he?

542
00:35:22,240 --> 00:35:22,960
Why don't I see him?

543
00:35:22,960 --> 00:35:23,600
I'm here.

544
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:24,460
Son, come here.

545
00:35:26,880 --> 00:35:27,520
Mr. Chen.

546
00:35:27,840 --> 00:35:28,770
Long time no see.

547
00:35:29,400 --> 00:35:30,000
Mrs. Chen.

548
00:35:31,560 --> 00:35:32,560
Good boy.

549
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:34,640
It's only been a few years,

550
00:35:34,640 --> 00:35:35,800
and you've grown so tall and handsome.

551
00:35:35,800 --> 00:35:36,600
Yes.

552
00:35:36,600 --> 00:35:37,600
I almost didn't recognize you.

553
00:35:37,600 --> 00:35:38,640
I grew up fast.

554
00:35:39,600 --> 00:35:41,200
Mr. Chen, you must be joking.

555
00:35:41,600 --> 00:35:42,400
That's great.

556
00:35:43,120 --> 00:35:44,080
Let's go inside.

557
00:35:44,360 --> 00:35:45,360
Please come in.

558
00:35:45,360 --> 00:35:46,160
Okay.

559
00:35:58,520 --> 00:35:58,960
Honey,

560
00:35:58,960 --> 00:36:00,160
I got the cake.

561
00:36:01,960 --> 00:36:03,560
Isn't this Jiang Lili?

562
00:36:04,040 --> 00:36:04,680
Long time no see.

563
00:36:04,680 --> 00:36:05,610
Long time no see.

564
00:36:06,240 --> 00:36:07,400
Xiaoxiao, you're so lucky.

565
00:36:07,400 --> 00:36:08,860
You get whatever you want.

566
00:36:09,200 --> 00:36:10,330
Is there none for us?

567
00:36:11,200 --> 00:36:12,520
Could a big internet celebrity like you

568
00:36:12,520 --> 00:36:13,720
eat this kind of stuff

569
00:36:13,720 --> 00:36:15,250
that we ordinary folks eat?

570
00:36:17,360 --> 00:36:19,000
Don't make fun of me.

571
00:36:19,120 --> 00:36:19,880
My few fans

572
00:36:19,880 --> 00:36:21,520
are nothing compared to Sister Aiwei's.

573
00:36:21,520 --> 00:36:23,200
It's the internet economy now.

574
00:36:23,200 --> 00:36:25,200
And you're in Aunt Aiwei's company.

575
00:36:25,200 --> 00:36:27,240
It's only a matter of time before you go viral.

576
00:36:27,240 --> 00:36:28,770
Thanks for your kind words.

577
00:36:29,480 --> 00:36:31,480
You have to treat our Xiaoxiao well.

578
00:36:31,640 --> 00:36:32,640
If he bullies you,

579
00:36:33,040 --> 00:36:33,560
tell me.

580
00:36:33,960 --> 00:36:34,560
No problem.

